name: Kirinyaga (Mount Kenya Spirit)
shortLoreBlurb: Kirinyaga (Mount Kenya Spirit) is a spirit from Kikuyu (Kenya) associated with mountain, ngai’s seat. Appeased for safe passage and rains.
overlapsLinks: Manannán (Celtic), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Tangaroa (Polynesia), Yemaya (Yoruba)
